text: The Seagull's Laughter () is a 2001 Icelandic German British drama movie directed by Ágúst Guðmundsson and starring Margrét Vilhjálmsdóttir, Ugla Egilsdóttir, Heino Ferch, Hilmir Snær Guðnason, Kristbjörg Kjeld. == Other websites == * Category:2001 drama movies Category:Icelandic movies Category:German drama movies Category:British drama movies Category:Movies directed by Ágúst Guðmundsson
title: The Seagull's Laughter
